&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>I need to give credit to Dan Held for publishing his 4-part series &lt;a href="https://medium.com/@danhedl/planting-bitcoin-sound-money-72e80e40ff62">comparing bitcoin’s origin to planting a tree&lt;/a>. While I loved his series, I believe a more robust analogy is comparing bitcoin to fungi. If you’re new to this topic, strap in — it is my honor to initiate you into the fascinating world of fungi.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>